result.name: Mixian Sense

reviews.text:
The place serves noodles and small side dishes. Majority of the soups have a spicy element to them from regular chili and numbing peppers. 
The noodles are quite good here and if you don't want to stand in line for 20 min, i suggest going there before 12 o'clock.
If You're Chinese you can just order via their app, there's a QR code for it on each table. If you don't read Chinese you can ask for an English menu, just make sure to double check your order after ordering, as most employees don't speak English and they will easily crew up your order
Very good selection of noodle. The Hoi Nan chicken and the pork chop were very good. You like spicy you come here.
Quite good overall. The tomato soup is very nice😋😋
Delicious rice noodle

Good location, great variety of rice noodles with affordable price. Considering its price, the taste and services were good enough. A-la-cart seems better than set menu, as you can choose noodles with own preference, without paying much more.

result.name: 米線陣

reviews.text:
只係一般。 比其他鋪佢嘅味道差。 塊豬扒都唔似以前有大漠風沙，而家只係叫有味。 其他湯 同米線都只係一般。 
仲見到隔離枱用手機落單，點知係會漏單，即係一係個客問題，一係個app問題，一係個介面問題。即係唔夠易用好用。

午餐食物清淡選擇多，
安排坐位的方式需要改善，兩人同行坐bar台，一人吃就搭枱
今天經過觀塘道鱷魚廣場嗰間(米線陣)。 品嚐咗一道麻辣擔擔豬扒米線。 好特別 擔擔麵食得多，麻辣擔擔豬扒米線。初試，夠份量，菜牌寫上麻辣醬湯底，只是微辣感覺，係微辣加上麻花香味，粉炸豬扒另上。價錢估唔到咁抵食。食客流量大搵位容易。
lunch黎幫襯過，款式幾多，食得出有心機煮個湯底，下次再同同事黎
地方不大，下午時段好坐。
